title: Hawkwind 2006-07-22 Gt Yarmouth - Eastern Haze Festival - MP3
description:
Great Yarmouth, Eastern Haze 2006 festival...

Hawkwind recordings morally belong to Hawkwind, and so should be circulated
only if they say it&#039;s OK. They haven&#039;t banned MP3s from circulating, and I believe
in letting Hawkwind reach everybody, not just those with money and fast cable 
connections.

So let those with slow internet connections download MP3 versions of shows: it&#039;s
only fair. Hawkwind is for the people!

OK, now that&#039;s the Commie crap out the way, let&#039;s get down to business.



QUALITY: 9.  This is GOOD!

Dave Brock, Alan Davey, Richard Chadwick, Jason Stuart, Mr.Dibs
